    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors reviewed under ASME V&V 40-2018 at Model Risk Level 5. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels, with gaps ranging from one to four gradations. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing substantive epistemic gaps. The package is accepted for archival and regulatory submission purposes under the Minimal profile; the credibility determination itself is Not Accepted pending resolution of factor gaps. No digital signature is present; package integrity is attested by the sha256 content hash only.",
